2011-07-08T11:11:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/best-friend-tech-june-sales-fall-37-42-table-5321-tt.html
BEST FRIEND TECH said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 37.42% to NT$58,650,000 from NT$93,721,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             58,650           93,721    
YOY%             -37.42%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            378,100          476,979    
YOY%             -20.73% 
=================================================================
 